these two sets of beautiful nails are from @klawbeauty !! i only show the application of the purple butterfly nails, but its the exact same for the white ones. these press-ons are very good quality and last up to 2 weeks! the application itself takes 10-15 minutes, and if a nail falls off, you can just re-glue it back on!! im having a much better experience with the white ones, but i think it’s because i applied them correctly whereas the purple ones lasted for only a week since i misapplied them. the seller recommends the following steps for application:
1. Use an alcohol wipe or nail polish remover to remove any oil + residue on nails.
2. Buff your nail well
3. Push back cuticles
4. Apply glue on the fake nail and press it onto your real nail!
—
i highly recommend you dm @klawbeauty for your own set so your nails can still look AMAZING & STUNNING over quarantine 😌💜
